{
  "content": "<p>With Isocyanates, eardiod proposes a 6 track EP of gritty techno. Organic and unexpected, most of eardiod's work is sequenced on the go, by hand on a setup mixing hardware boxes and software synthesizers. Echoing from the remnants of Stockholm's underground scene, this release takes you on a trip to basement raves where lasers pierce the smoke.</p>",
